Package com.gabrielbauman.jwp4j

Interface JsonProofAlgorithmResolver

public interface JsonProofAlgorithmResolver
This interface is used by JsonWebProof during deserialization to find a JsonWebAlgorithm implementation that can handle the "alg" claim specified by its issuer header.

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type
    Method
    Description
    JsonProofAlgorithm
    resolve(String alg)
    Resolve a JsonProofAlgorithm instance using an 'alg' identifier.

    • resolve

      JsonProofAlgorithm resolve(String alg)
      Resolve a JsonProofAlgorithm instance using an 'alg' identifier.
      Parameters:
      alg - the string identifier representing a JsonProofAlgorithm.
      Returns:
      a usable instance of a JsonProofAlgorithm that can handle JWPs with the specified alg value.
